  "text": "The procedure of the preliminary GAPDH denaturation and its separation into fractions as well as SH-SY5Y cell culturing conditions are described in detail in a related article [CITATION_1] . Therefore, we used 3 GAPDH fractions: to verify the aggregate content in each fraction we applied ultrafiltration through acetate cellulose membrane (Fig. 1) as described earlier [CITATION_2] . To explore the dynamics of apoptosis, the cells were placed in a 96-well micro-titre plate, and acridine orange in phosphate-buffered saline was added to a concentration of 5 μg/mL. Stained cells were analysed with the aid of a Zeiss Axioscope (Zeiss, Jena, Germany) (Figs. 2 and 3) . ",
